OL,3,CPlans for new Heysel memorial at
OL,4,CAnfield unveiled by Liverpool
OL,6,FLiverpool Football Club have unveiled
OL,7,Fplans for a new memorial to the Heysel
OL,8,Fdisaster to mark the 40th anniversary
OL,9,Fof the event.
OL,11,F39 people were killed when a wall
OL,12,Fcollapsed at the stadium in Belgium
OL,13,Fahead of Liverpool's European Cup
OL,14,Ffinal against Juventus on 29 May 1985,
OL,15,Fmost of them were Italian fans.
OL,17,FThe new memorial will be named Forever
OL,18,FBound and will replace the current
OL,19,Fplaque at Anfield later this summer.
