OL,3,CPlans for new Heysel memorial at
OL,4,CAnfield unveiled by Liverpool
OL,6,FFeaturing two scarves knotted together
OL,7,Fand gently tied - symbolising the
OL,8,Funity and solidarity between Liverpool
OL,9,Fand Juventus in the aftermath of the
OL,10,Fdisaster - the memorial also includes
OL,11,Fan inscription alongside the names of
OL,12,Fthe 39 supporters who died.
OL,14,FIan Rush, who played for both clubs
OL,15,Fand was in the Liverpool side on that
OL,16,Fnight said: "To see a new memorial
OL,17,Fcreated with such care means a lot and
OL,18,Fit's incredibly important to have a
OL,19,Ffitting tribute to remember the 39
OL,20,Ffans who lost their lives.
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                    G2/6
