OL,3,CPlans for new Heysel memorial at
OL,4,CAnfield unveiled by Liverpool
OL,6,F"We must never forget why this
OL,7,Fmatters, and why we continue to stand
OL,8,Ftogether in solidarity, all these
OL,9,Fyears later."
OL,11,FJonathan Bamber, Liverpool's chief
OL,12,Flegal and external affairs officer and
OL,13,Fexecutive sponsor of Forever Reds
OL,14,Fstresses that all effort were made to
OL,15,Fgather the views of those directly
OL,16,Faffected before going ahead:"If
OL,17,FJuventus didn't want us to do that, or
OL,18,Fif the families of those that lost
OL,19,Ftheir lives didn't want us to do that,
OL,20,Fthen we wouldn't have.
