OL,3,CPlans for new Heysel memorial at
OL,4,CAnfield unveiled by Liverpool
OL,6,F"I'm pleased to say that they have
OL,7,Fgiven...consent, if you will, and I'm
OL,8,Falso happy to say that officials from
OL,9,FJuventus will be over at Anfield when
OL,10,Fwe unveil the new memorial later this
OL,11,Fsummer. "
OL,13,FHe adds: "The Heysel disaster is a
OL,14,Fsignificant chapter in our history,
OL,15,Fand one which we must never forget.
OL,17,F"It's important that we honour those
OL,18,Fwho lost their lives with a memorial
OL,19,Fthat reflects the depth of our respect
OL,20,Fand remembrance."
