OL,3,CPlans for new Heysel memorial at
OL,4,CAnfield unveiled by Liverpool
OL,6,FThe club says that the current
OL,7,Fmemorial is situated on the Sir Kenny
OL,8,FDalglish Stand and that its
OL,9,Freplacement will be mounted to a new
OL,10,Flocation at the ground to offer a more
OL,11,Faccessible space to remember those
OL,12,Finvolved, though a final decision on
OL,13,Fthe new site hasn't yet been finalised.
OL,15,FLiverpool chief executive officer
OL,16,FBilly Hogan and club ambassador Rush
OL,17,Fwill attend the unveiling of Juventus'
OL,18,Fnew Heysel memorial, 'Verso Altrove',
OL,19,Fin Turin as part of the 40th
OL,20,Fanniversary commemorations.
