OL,6,F'Verso Altrove' will be unveiled on
OL,7,Fthe 40th anniversary of the disaster
OL,8,Fon May 29.
OL,10,FLiverpool have said, out of respect of
OL,11,Fthat, 'Forever Bound' will be
OL,12,Fofficially unveiled later in the
OL,13,Fsummer at a location to be agreed
OL,14,Ffollowing consultation with key
OL,15,Fstakeholders.
